The People of the State of New York ex rel. Carlos Rodriguez, Appellant, v. J. Edwin La Vallee, as Warden of Clinton Prison, Respondent. Submitted September 28, 1964; decided October 1, 1964. Carlos Rodriguez, pro se, for motion.

No one opposed.

Motion dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from does not finally determine the proceeding within the meaning of the Constitution.
